div.p:
We do likewiſe Preſent, that Factious Coffee-men, Victuallers, and Ale-houſe-Keepers in this Borough, have greatly contributed to our late Diviſions;
and that divers of them do ſtill continue to make their Houſes the Receptacles of Diſloyal and ill-affected Perſons in ſuſpicious numbers:
Notwithſtanding their entire dependence upon his Majeſties Grace and Bounty, for the Livelihood of Themſelves, and their Families.
